dcterms:description: A lightweight environment developed for simulating the gripper of the SOTO2 robot, allowing for the testing of control algorithms under irregular and asynchronous conditions.
dcterms:title: PyBullet Environment

dcterms:description: A simulation environment for the Turtlebot3 robot, utilizing ROS2 for asynchronous communications with the controller, allowing for testing of control strategies in a realistic setting.
dcterms:title: Gazebo Turtlebot3 Simulation

dcterms:description: Offline logs from the SOTO2 robot operating at customer sites, capturing various operational data for meta-learning experiments.
dcterms:title: SOTO2 Robot Offline Logs

dcterms:description: Distribution of box properties used in experiments, detailing the mass and inertial characteristics of boxes manipulated by the SOTO2 robot.
dcterms:title: Box Distribution P(Tbox)

dcterms:description: Distribution of dynamics properties for the Turtlebot3 robot, used in experiments to evaluate control strategies under varying physical conditions.
dcterms:title: Dynamics Distribution P(Tturtle)
